程序包 org.tron.trident.core.contract

类 ContractFunction

java.lang.Object
org.tron.trident.core.contract.ContractFunction
public class ContractFunction extends Object
The class ContractFunction provides a easier way to access smart contract functions.

With a ContractFunction object, it's easy for users to see the function declaration and easy to call by construct a Function

从以下版本开始:
jdk 1.8.0_231
